  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This Nindo is one of tenacity. When an ally has fallen unconscious after falling to 0 Hit points and you are outnumbered. You gain advantage to attack rolls and Dexterity Saves for the next minute. If you pass the Dexterity save while this Nindo is active, you ignore the effects entirely. You can gain the benefit of this effect, once per long rest</p>",
